Hi, Veekiwi,
After my Covid I had really painful headaches. My neurologist gave me the diagnose migraine. He gave me MagnesioCard. It was good. My doctor for the neurorehabilitation told me, that my headaches means that is it too much for my brain. It needs a brake. I tried it. When I got headaches I switched off the light, didn't play music, went to bed, did nothing and it helped. So I learned how many I could do and when my body needs a brake. All the best!
